text: Mohsin Ahmad Alaini () (20 October 1932 - 25 August 2021) was a Yemeni politician. He was the Prime Minister of the Yemen Arab Republic five times between 1967 and 1975. Al-Aini was the first Foreign Minister of the Yemen Arab Republic.
